docs {
  # Limit Order Market Simulator — REST API

  This Bruno collection covers the full REST API of the trading simulator.

  ---

  ## Quick Start

  ### 1. Start the backend
  ```bash
  cd /path/to/limit-order-market-simulator
  python -m src.server.server
  ```
  Server runs on **http://localhost:8888**.

  ### 2. Select an environment
  In Bruno, select the **Local** environment (top-right corner).

  ### 3. Register / Log in
  Run `auth → Register`, then `auth → Login`.
  The token is saved automatically into the `{{accessToken}}` variable — all protected requests will use it automatically.

  ---

  ## Authentication

  | Token | Stored in | TTL |
  |-------|-----------|-----|
  | **Access token** (JWT) | Bruno variable `accessToken` | 15 minutes |
  | **Refresh token** | HttpOnly cookie `refresh_token` | 7 days |

  When the access token expires, run `auth → Refresh Token` — you will receive a new token and the cookie is rotated automatically.

  ---

  ## Endpoints

  ### 🔐 Auth
  | Seq | Request | Method | URL | Auth |
  |-----|---------|--------|-----|------|
  | 1 | Register | POST | `/api/auth/register` | — |
  | 2 | Login | POST | `/api/auth/login` | — |
  | 3 | Refresh Token | POST | `/api/auth/refresh` | cookie |
  | 4 | Me | GET | `/api/auth/me` | Bearer |
  | 5 | Logout | POST | `/api/auth/logout` | cookie |

  ### 📈 Market (public)
  | Seq | Request | Method | URL |
  |-----|---------|--------|-----|
  | 1 | Products | GET | `/api/market/products` |
  | 2 | Order Book | GET | `/api/market/orderbook?product=&depth=` |
  | 3 | Report | GET | `/api/market/report?product=&history_len=` |

  ### 📋 Orders (Bearer token required)
  | Seq | Request | Method | URL |
  |-----|---------|--------|-----|
  | 1 | Place Order | POST | `/api/orders` |
  | 2 | Get Order | GET | `/api/orders/:orderId?product=` |
  | 3 | Modify Order | PATCH | `/api/orders/:orderId` |
  | 4 | Cancel Order | DELETE | `/api/orders/:orderId?product=` |

  ### 👤 Account (Bearer token required)
  | Seq | Request | Method | URL |
  |-----|---------|--------|-----|
  | 1 | Balance | GET | `/api/account/balance?product=` |
  | 2 | My Orders | GET | `/api/account/orders?product=` |

  ---

  ## Variables

  | Variable | Description | Set by |
  |----------|-------------|--------|
  | `baseUrl` | Server base URL | Environment (Local / Production) |
  | `product` | Product name | Environment |
  | `accessToken` | JWT access token | Automatically after Login / Refresh |
  | `userId` | User trading UUID | Automatically after Login |
  | `orderId` | Last placed order ID | Automatically after Place Order |

  ---

  ## Recommended Testing Flow

  ```
  Register → Login → Products → Order Book → Place Order → Get Order → Modify Order → Cancel Order → Balance → My Orders → Logout
  ```
}
